IN THE HIGH COURT OF JUDICATURE AT BOMBAY
 ORIDINARY ORIGINAL CIVIL JURISDICTION
SUIT NO. 728 OF 1989
 Bank of Maharashtra ........Plaintiffs
versus
 J.K. Pendharkar ........Defendant.
 Mr. Sachin Joshi adv. for the Plaintiffs
 None for the Defendants

CORAM: A. P. DESHPANDE, J.
DATED : 06th MAY, 2009.
P.C.:
.
Perused the order dated 25-9-1992. Despite grant of
sufficient time, no written statement was filed ad thus the suit
came to be decreed under Order 8 Rule 10 of Code of Civil
Procedure. In view of the disposal of the suit nothing survives
now.

(A. P. DESHPANDE, J.)
